'''Ssi-ruuvi''' was the language used by the [[Ssi-ruu]]k from the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Lwhekk/Legends|Lwhekk]]. It could not be reproduced by [[Human/Legends|Humans]], who did not possess the organs needed to do so.

It was formed by melodic clicks and whistles. When spoken it was considered similar to the sound of a flute, which caused the Ssi-ruuk to be nicknamed "Fluties".

It was rare for a Ssi-ruuk to learn other languages, preferring to use translators. As Ssi-ruuvi was not a very extended language, only their own translators were fluent in both Ssi-ruuvi and [[Galactic Basic Standard/Legends|Basic]]

